local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

local this = UIComponent(Address)
function OnSelect() if this:CurrentState() ~= "inactive" then local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("mp_battle3_scenario")) parent:LuaCall("SaveSetup") end end

local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent())
local Faction = nil local Alliance = nil local Army = nil
function Initialise(f, a, ai) --out.tom("Initialising", this:Id(), f, a, ai)
Faction = f Alliance = a Army = ai end
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("NotifyFactionSelected", Faction, Alliance, Army) end
